;How do I turn off Location-Aware Browsing permanently?
Co poss jau deactivar permanentamain Location-Aware Browsing?


;Location-Aware Browsing is always opt-in in Firefox. No location information is ever sent without your permission. If you wish to disable the feature completely, please follow this set of steps:
Location-Aware Browsing pretenda en Firefox adina ina conferma da l’utilisader. Naginas infurmaziuns davart tia posiziun vegnan communitgadas senza tia permissiun. Sche ti vuls deactivar cumplettamain questa funcziun, suonda per plaschair ils suandants pass:


;In the URL bar, type <code>about:config</code>
Scriva <code>about:config</code> en la trav d’adressas


;Type <code>geo.enabled</code>
Endatescha <code>geo.enabled</code>


;Double click on the <em>geo.enabled</em> preference
Clicca duas giadas sin la preferenza <em>geo.enabled</em>


;Location-Aware Browsing is now disabled
Location-Aware Browsing è ussa deactivà


